{"tid":1953640,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"元朗721恐怖襲擊7被告下午再提訊 首被告不認罪 其餘6名正考慮意向","createTime":"2020-04-01T09:42:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-01T13:44:37.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"48d6083ba68b5bf75bcbafc33dc4287d1e749494","tid":1953640,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T09:42:46.000Z","msg":"元朗721暴力襲擊7被告下午再提訊<br />\n<br />\n去年7月21日西鐵元朗站暴力襲擊事件，7名涉案男子合共被控三項暴動罪及三項串謀有意圖而傷人罪，下午於區域法院再提訊，法官批准將兩案合併處理，並押後至6月9號再訊，五名被告以原有條件續保，其餘兩名被告則繼續還押。<br />\n<br />\n首被告王志榮透過律師表示，打算不認罪，其他被告則仍在考慮答辯意向，或正在申請法援。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1278094&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1278094%26csid%3D261_341&d=fPi9TpucIiEDTgLGk%2FOmnR1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=d08b1bb3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1278094&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"1aa544e0f3fcb50de8149f96f991e80f84a98a84","tid":1953640,"uid":304856,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T09:56:49.000Z","msg":"左邊告，右邊放<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁多紅官<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98df384a796d3743afbd3a8d86d5555a0b88477b","tid":1953640,"uid":227628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T13:44:37.000Z","msg":"有曬片點到佢唔認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}